        </svg>
      </span>
      <span><strong>The cleanup would contain and remove lead-based paint in debris from the site.</strong></span>
    </p>

    <p>DTSC proposes:</p>
    <ul>
    <li>Removing debris</li>
    <li>Sampling soil beneath debris</li>
    <li>Removing contaminated soil as necessary</li>
    <li>Potentially restricting what can be built on the site after cleanup</li>
    </ul>

